data.description: You will love this beautiful move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with open floor concept and cathedral ceilings on 1.73+/- acres!  Come see this home for your self and fall in love! This home is spacious and has room for everyone including an extra room that can be used as a den or dinning room.  The upstairs has 2 bedrooms and a jack and jill bathroom.  If you are handy, it also has a 16x20 outdoor building for all your handy projects. It is  nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac with a huge backyard to enjoy warm summer nights! It also has a brand new HVAC unit. Country setting but it is also convenient to highways, shopping and dinning. Schedule your showing today!
